0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n이미지 출처: (<a href=\"https://muhaddis.info/automate-the-code-formatting-with-eslint-and-prettier/\">https://muhaddis.info/automate-the-code-formatting-with-eslint-and-prettier/</a>)</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-eslint와-prettier\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-eslint%EC%99%80-prettier\" aria-label=\"1 eslint와 prettier permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. ESLint와 Prettier</h3>\n<h4 id=\"eslint와-prettier를-사용해야-하는-이유\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#eslint%EC%99%80-prettier%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0\" aria-label=\"eslint와 prettier를 사용해야 하는 이유 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>❓ESLint와 Prettier를 사용해야 하는 이유</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>프로젝트에 참여하는 개발자들은 각기 코딩 스타일이 다르다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>그래서 다른 스타일을 가진 개발자가 코드를 보려면 피로도가 증가한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>팀원과의 소통을 통해 어느정도 정할 수 있다고 해도, 그 갯수가 계속해서 증가한다면 한계가 생긴다.</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>코드 스타일 자동화를 통해 이를 해결할 수 있다. 이를 도와주는 대표적인 도구가 ESLint, Prettier이다.</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"2-eslint\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-eslint\" aria-label=\"2 eslint permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. ESLint</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>일관된 코드를 보장해주는 것이 ESLint의 역할이다.</li>\n<li>코드의 구문을 분석하여 버그 발생의 여지가 있는 코드, 불필요한 코드, 위험성이 존재하는 코드 등에 대한 경고를 출력해준다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"2-1-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-1-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 1 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-1. 설치</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 개발 환경에서만 사용하기 때문에 --save-dev 옵션을 넣는다.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># CRA로 프로젝트를 시작할 경우, 내장되어 있기 때문에 설치하지 않아도 된다.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> eslint --save-dev\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># eslint에는 formatting 관련된 rule도 있는데,</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 이 경우 prettier와 다른 설정을 가지고 있다면 설정 충돌이 발생한다.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 이를 방지하기 위해 eslint-config-prettier를 사용한다.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> eslint-config-prettier --save-dev</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"2-2-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-2-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"2 2 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2-2. 설정</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>루트 디렉토리에 <strong>.eslintrc.확장자</strong> 파일을 통해 설정이 가능하다.</li>\n<li>처음부터 모든 설정을 하는것이 불편하다면 다른 사람들이 정의해준 config 플러그인을 설치하여 사용할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">ex<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"parser\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@typescript-eslint/parser\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"plugins\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"@typescript-eslint\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-hooks\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 플러그인을 추가한다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"extends\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 규칙 확장 플러그인을 넣는다.</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"airbnb\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:react/recommended\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:jsx-a11y/recommended\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:import/errors\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:import/warnings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"plugin:prettier/recommended\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"prettier\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"prettier/prettier\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"rules\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 규칙을 설정한다.</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"no-alert\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"off\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"react/jsx-filename-extension\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"warn\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string-property property\">\"extensions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\".tsx\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"import/extensions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token string\">\"error\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token string\">\"ignorePackages\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"ts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"never\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"tsx\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"never\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> \n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"settings\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"import/resolver\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"typescript\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-prettier\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-prettier\" aria-label=\"3 prettier permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Prettier</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>코드의 Formatting을 담당한다.</li>\n<li>줄 바꿈, 공백, 들여 쓰기 등 에디터에서의 텍스트 일관성을 보장해준다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"3-1-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-1-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"3 1 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-1. 설치</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 개발 환경에서만 사용하기 때문에 --save-dev 옵션을 넣는다.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> prettier --save-dev</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"3-2-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-2-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"3 2 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-2. 설정</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>루트 디렉토리에 <strong>.prettierrc.확장자</strong> 파일을 통해 설정이 가능하다.</li>\n<li>사용가능한 옵션은 (<a href=\"https://prettier.io/docs/en/options.html\">https://prettier.io/docs/en/options.html</a>)를 참고한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ex<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"singleQuote\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> true, // 홑따옴표 사용\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"semi\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> true, // 세미콜론 사용\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"useTabs\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> true, // 탭 사용\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"printWidth\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">120</span> // 너비\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<p>📂 <strong>참고자료</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://velog.io/@jiynn_12/%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90%EB%A1%9C-%ED%98%91%EC%97%85%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-Eslint-prettier-husy-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">jiynn_12님 블로그</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"✔ 협업을 위한 ESLint, Prettier \n이미지 출처: (https://muhaddis.info/automate-the-code-formatting-with-eslint-and-prettier/) 1. ESLint와 Prettier ❓ESLint와 Prettier를 사용해야 하는 이유 프로젝트에 참여하는 개발자들은 각기 코딩 스타일이 다르다. 그래서 다른 스타일을 가진 개발자가 코드를 보려면 피로도가 증가한다. 팀원과의 소통을 통해 어느정도 정할 수 있다고 해도, 그 갯수가 계속해서 증가한다면 한계가 생긴다. 코드 스타일 자동화를 통해 이를 해결할 수 있다. 이를 도와주는 대표적인 도구가 ESLint, Prettier이다. 2. ESLint 일관된 코드를 보장해주는 것이 ESLint의 역할이다. 코드의 구문을 분석하여 버그 발생의 여지가 있는 코드, 불필요한 코드, 위험성이 존재하는 코드 등에 대한 경고를 출력해준다. 2-1. 설치 2-2. 설정 루트 디렉토리에 .eslin…","frontmatter":{"date":"August 26, 2023","title":"협업을 위한 ESLint, Prettier","categories":"work","author":"이용민"},"fields":{"slug":"/work/eslint-prettier/"}},"next":{"id":"62a0fabf-49c7-51b6-9dee-1555645ebd57","html":"<h2 id=\"-구글-클라우드google-cloud-platform로-https-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EA%B5%AC%EA%B8%80-%ED%81%B4%EB%9D%BC%EC%9A%B0%EB%93%9Cgoogle-cloud-platform%EB%A1%9C-https-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\" 구글 클라우드google cloud platform로 https 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔ 구글 클라우드(Google Cloud Platform)로 HTTPS 적용하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-인스턴스-그룹-만들기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%9D%B8%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B4%EC%8A%A4-%EA%B7%B8%EB%A3%B9-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 인스턴스 그룹 만들기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 인스턴스 그룹 만들기</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.55555555555555%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"인스턴스 그룹 만들기\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5cd90346b95b1170cf87c1bc28cc8a59/37523/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5cd90346b95b1170cf87c1bc28cc8a59/e9ff0/image.png 180w,\n/static/5cd90346b95b1170cf87c1bc28cc8a59/f21e7/image.png 360w,\n/static/5cd90346b95b1170cf87c1bc28cc8a59/37523/image.png 720w,\n/static/5cd90346b95b1170cf87c1bc28cc8a59/302a4/image.png 1080w,\n/static/5cd90346b95b1170cf87c1bc28cc8a59/07a9c/image.png 1440w,\n/static/5cd90346b95b1170cf87c1bc28cc8a59/b85c3/image.png 2580w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Compute Engine 메뉴 > 인스턴스 그룹 메뉴 >  인스턴스 그룹 만들기 버튼 클릭 > New unmanaged instance group 메뉴에서 위와 같이 생성한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-고정-ip-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EA%B3%A0%EC%A0%95-ip-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 고정 ip 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 고정 IP 생성</h3>\n<p>고정 IP를 생성해야한다.<br>\n<a href=\"https://slowteady.github.io/infra/gcp-02/\">3. 고정 IP 설정 참고</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-부하-분산기-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EB%B6%80%ED%95%98-%EB%B6%84%EC%82%B0%EA%B8%B0-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"3 부하 분산기 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 부하 분산기 생성</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.888888888888886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"부하 분산기 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5e04ec8a5bab480d485a5fb903a1c50b/37523/image-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5e04ec8a5bab480d485a5fb903a1c50b/e9ff0/image-1.png 180w,\n/static/5e04ec8a5bab480d485a5fb903a1c50b/f21e7/image-1.png 360w,\n/static/5e04ec8a5bab480d485a5fb903a1c50b/37523/image-1.png 720w,\n/static/5e04ec8a5bab480d485a5fb903a1c50b/302a4/image-1.png 1080w,\n/static/5e04ec8a5bab480d485a5fb903a1c50b/07a9c/image-1.png 1440w,\n/static/5e04ec8a5bab480d485a5fb903a1c50b/41045/image-1.png 2434w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>네트워크 서비스 메뉴 > 부하분산 메뉴로 이동하여 HTTPS로 부하 분산기를 생성한다.<br>\n그리고 백엔드, 프론트엔드를 구성해야한다.<br>\n백엔드, 프론트엔드 구성 후 부하 분산기 생성을 하면 HTTPS 적용까지 시간이 다소 소요된다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-1-백엔드-구성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-1-%EB%B0%B1%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"3 1 백엔드 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-1. 백엔드 구성</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.555555555555554%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"백엔드 구성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8b39187910b5a07e13741ebf2d32c54d/37523/image-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8b39187910b5a07e13741ebf2d32c54d/e9ff0/image-2.png 180w,\n/static/8b39187910b5a07e13741ebf2d32c54d/f21e7/image-2.png 360w,\n/static/8b39187910b5a07e13741ebf2d32c54d/37523/image-2.png 720w,\n/static/8b39187910b5a07e13741ebf2d32c54d/302a4/image-2.png 1080w,\n/static/8b39187910b5a07e13741ebf2d32c54d/07a9c/image-2.png 1440w,\n/static/8b39187910b5a07e13741ebf2d32c54d/1a238/image-2.png 3294w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>위의 메뉴에서 백엔드 서비스 만들기를 클릭한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 185%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"백엔드 서비스 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/057532dbb05efd7f71ff05b18fd7f165/37523/image-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/057532dbb05efd7f71ff05b18fd7f165/e9ff0/image-3.png 180w,\n/static/057532dbb05efd7f71ff05b18fd7f165/f21e7/image-3.png 360w,\n/static/057532dbb05efd7f71ff05b18fd7f165/37523/image-3.png 720w,\n/static/057532dbb05efd7f71ff05b18fd7f165/1568e/image-3.png 892w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>이름 입력 후, 인스턴스 그룹에 생성했던 그룹을 넣는다.<br>\nCloud CDN의 상태 확인에는 기본값인 webrtc-healthcheck을 넣고 생성한다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-2-프론트엔드-구성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-2-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%A0%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"3 2 프론트엔드 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-2. 프론트엔드 구성</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"프론트엔드 구성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5e1c302588260d3994ab7710680fd293/37523/image-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5e1c302588260d3994ab7710680fd293/e9ff0/image-5.png 180w,\n/static/5e1c302588260d3994ab7710680fd293/f21e7/image-5.png 360w,\n/static/5e1c302588260d3994ab7710680fd293/37523/image-5.png 720w,\n/static/5e1c302588260d3994ab7710680fd293/302a4/image-5.png 1080w,\n/static/5e1c302588260d3994ab7710680fd293/07a9c/image-5.png 1440w,\n/static/5e1c302588260d3994ab7710680fd293/1cb21/image-5.png 2586w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 147.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"인증서 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f5fc28b65aafd17fde1ebfb58c7dd13c/37523/image-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f5fc28b65aafd17fde1ebfb58c7dd13c/e9ff0/image-6.png 180w,\n/static/f5fc28b65aafd17fde1ebfb58c7dd13c/f21e7/image-6.png 360w,\n/static/f5fc28b65aafd17fde1ebfb58c7dd13c/37523/image-6.png 720w,\n/static/f5fc28b65aafd17fde1ebfb58c7dd13c/f0551/image-6.png 862w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>만들어놓은 고정 IP주소를 넣고 프로토콜을 HTTPS로 설정한다.<br>\n인증서 만들기에서 만들어놓은 도메인을 넣어 인증서를 생성한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"4 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 확인</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"완료\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d695b1cb39a3ebe23f755ad41fd9c17a/6af66/image-7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d695b1cb39a3ebe23f755ad41fd9c17a/e9ff0/image-7.png 180w,\n/static/d695b1cb39a3ebe23f755ad41fd9c17a/f21e7/image-7.png 360w,\n/static/d695b1cb39a3ebe23f755ad41fd9c17a/6af66/image-7.png 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>부하 분산기 생성 후 적용까지 시간이 많이 소요된다.<br>\n기다렸다가 적용이 완료됐는지 확인한다.</p>\n<hr>","frontmatter":{"date":"August 12, 2023","title":"구글 클라우드(GCP)으로 HTTPS 적용하기","categories":"infra","author":"이용민"},"fields":{"slug":"/infra/gcp-03/"}},"prev":{"id":"d8f1b1a6-2bcb-5981-81cf-378473390ba1","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 132.22222222222223%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Git-flow\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/691792b62b28811138bfebe74ffef56d/37523/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/691792b62b28811138bfebe74ffef56d/e9ff0/image.png 180w,\n/static/691792b62b28811138bfebe74ffef56d/f21e7/image.png 360w,\n/static/691792b62b28811138bfebe74ffef56d/37523/image.png 720w,\n/static/691792b62b28811138bfebe74ffef56d/302a4/image.png 1080w,\n/static/691792b62b28811138bfebe74ffef56d/07a9c/image.png 1440w,\n/static/691792b62b28811138bfebe74ffef56d/e8950/image.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n출처: (<a href=\"https://nvie.com/posts/a-successful-git-branching-model/\">https://nvie.com/posts/a-successful-git-branching-model/</a>)</p>\n<h2 id=\"-git-flow\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-git-flow\" aria-label=\" git flow permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✔ Git-flow</h2>\n<h3 id=\"git-flow-란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#git-flow-%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"git flow 란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Git-flow 란?</h3>\n<p>Git-flow는 대중적으로 많이 사용되는 개발 작업 절차이자 방법론 중 하나이다.<br>\nGit-flow 방식을 사용할 경우, 체계적이고 효율적으로 프로젝트를 관리할 수 있다.<br>\n브랜치를 이용한 프로젝트 관리 방식이다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"branch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#branch\" aria-label=\"branch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Branch</h3>\n<p>Git-flow에서 사용되는 대표적인 브랜치는 아래와 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>main: 프로덕트로 배포할 수 있는 브랜치</li>\n<li>develop: 프로덕트가 되기 전의 개발 버전을 다루는 브랜치</li>\n<li>feature: 단위별로 기능을 개발하는 브랜치</li>\n<li>release: main 브랜치로 병합 전에 QA를 통해 버그를 찾아내기 위한 브랜치</li>\n<li>hotfixes: 버그가 발생했을 경우, 빠르게 버그를 수정하기 위한 브랜치</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"순서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%88%9C%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"순서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>순서</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>main 브랜치와 develop 브랜치로 시작한다.</li>\n<li>feature 브랜치를 생성하여 기능을 개발하고 develop 브랜치에 병합한다.</li>\n<li>이번 버전에 필요한 기능이 모두 개발 되었다면 QA를 위해 release 브랜치를 생성한다.</li>\n<li>release 브랜치에서 QA 진행 후 develop 브랜치와 main 브랜치에 병합한다.</li>\n<li>main 브랜치에서 버그 발생 시 hotfixes 브랜치를 생성하여 버그 수정 후 main, develop 브랜치에 병합한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>브랜치와 순서는 절대적이지 않다.<br>\n팀원들과의 소통을 통해 유연하게 컨벤션을 맞추는 것이 옳은 방향이다.</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<p>📂 <strong>참고자료</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chanyeong.com/blog/post/15\">chanyeong님 블로그</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"August 26, 2023","title":"협업을 위한 Git-flow","categories":"git","author":"이용민"},"fields":{"slug":"/git/git-01/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://slowteady.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/work/eslint-prettier/","nextSlug":"/infra/gcp-03/","prevSlug":"/git/git-01/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"],"slicesMap":{}}